swagger: "2.0"
layout: system/spec-renderer.html
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: Swagger Petstore
  license:
    name: MIT
host: petstore.swagger.io
basePath: /v1
schemes:
  - http
consumes:
  - application/json
produces:
  - application/json
paths:
  /pets:
    get:
      summary: List all pets
      operationId: listPets
      tags:
        - pets
      parameters:
        - name: limit
          in: query
          description: How many items to return at one time (max 100)
          required: false
          type: integer
          format: int32
      responses:
        "200":
          description: A paged array of pets
          headers:
            x-next:
              type: string
              description: A link to the next page of responses
          schema:
            $ref: '#/definitions/Pets'
        default:
          description: unexpected error
          schema:
            $ref: '#/definitions/Error'
    post:
      summary: Create a pet
      operationId: createPets
      tags:
        - pets
      responses:
        "201":
          description: Null response
        default:
          description: unexpected error
          schema:
            $ref: '#/definitions/Error'
  /pets/{petId}:
    get:
      summary: Info for a specific pet
      operationId: showPetById
      tags:
        - pets
      parameters:
        - name: petId
          in: path
          required: true
          description: The id of the pet to retrieve
          type: string
      responses:
        "200":
          description: Expected response to a valid request
          schema:
            $ref: '#/definitions/Pets'
        default:
          description: unexpected error
          schema:
            $ref: '#/definitions/Error'
definitions:
  Pet:
    type: "object"
    required:
      - id
      - name
    properties:
      id:
        type: integer
        format: int64
      name:
        type: string
      tag:
        type: string
  Pets:
    type: array
    items:
      $ref: '#/definitions/Pet'
  Error:
    type: "object"
    required:
      - code
      - message
    properties:
      code:
        type: integer
        format: int32
      message:
        type: string

name: Kong
fonts:
  base: Roboto
  code: Roboto Mono
  headings: Lato
colors:
  header:
    value: '#FFFFFF'
    description: Background for header
  page:
    value: '#FFFFFF'
    description: Background on pages
  hero:
    value: '#003459'
    description: 'Background for hero text on hompage, about, login, contact us...'
  text_hero:
    value: '#FFFFFF'
    description: 'Text on top of hero, used on homepage, about, login, contact us...'
  footer:
    value: '#F7F9FA'
    description: Background on footer
  accent:
    value: '#57BBD6'
    description: Borders and catalog preview icons
  text_primary:
    value: '#404040'
    description: Main text
  text_secondary:
    value: '#8C8C8C'
    description: 'Supporting text, hints, etc.'
  text_headings:
    value: '#005999'
    description: Headings
  text_links:
    value: '#1782CF'
    descrption: Link color
  button_primary_fill:
    value: '#3FA66A'
    description: Background for Primary Button
  button_primary_fill_hover:
    value: '#3DCC91'
    description: Hover background for Primary Button
  button_primary_text:
    value: '#FFFFFF'
    description: Text for Primary Button
  button_secondary_fill:
    description: Background for Secondary Button
    value: '#FFFFFF'
  button_secondary_fill_hover:
    description: Hover background for Secondary Button
    value: '#F0F9FF'
  button_secondary_border:
    description: Border Secondary Button
    value: '#A3D9FF'
  button_secondary_text:
    description: Text for Secondary Button
    value: '#21A66F'
images:
  logo: assets/images/logo-developers-light.svg

.table-header {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}
.table-header button {
    font-size: 1rem;
    padding: .25rem 1rem .5rem;
    margin-left: auto;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
    border-radius: 0.25rem;
    border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
    background-color: #f5f5f5;
    transition: all 0.2s ease-in-out;
    cursor: pointer;
}
.table-header button span {
      color: #0A7BCC;
      font-weight: 800;
}
.table-header button:hover {
      color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85);
      border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
}
.table-header button:active {
      color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
      background-color: gainsboro;
}
.credential-list {
  margin-bottom: 36px;
}
.credential-table {
  overflow-x: auto;
}
.credential-table tbody {
    border-bottom: 1px solid #dee2e6;
}
.credential-table .table-actions {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: flex-end;
}
.credential-table .table-actions a {
      color: #2978CA;
      cursor: pointer;
}
.credential-table .table-actions a:not(:last-child) {
        margin: 0 1rem;
}
.credential-table .table-actions a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
}
.credential-table .table-actions svg {
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 300ms ease;
}
.credential-table .table-actions svg:hover path {
        fill: #E67E7E;
}
.credential-table .modal-dialog p {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
}
.credential-table .modal-dialog p strong {
      color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85);
}
.credential-table .modal-dialog p.light {
      color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.45);
}
.empty-credentials-wrapper {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  padding: 2rem 0;
  background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.03);
}
.empty-credentials-wrapper h3 {
    margin-bottom: .5rem;
    font-size: 17px;
    font-weight: normal;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
}
.empty-credentials-wrapper p {
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
}

.field:not(:first-child) {
  padding-top: 16px;
}
.field p {
  margin: 2px 0;
  font-size: 13px;
  letter-spacing: 0;
  line-height: 20px;
}
.field p:not(.helper) {
    text-transform: capitalize;
}
.field p.helper {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.45);
    font-style: italic;
}

    font-weight: 600;
    color: #f2110d;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-style: italic;

.k-toaster[data-v-5e0ed801] {
  position: fixed;
  top: 50px;
  right: 0;
  z-index: 10000;
  width: 300px;
  padding-left: 10px;
  padding-right: 10px;
}
.k-toaster .k-toast[data-v-5e0ed801] {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
  padding: 1rem;
  border: 1px solid;
  border-radius: 8px;
  color: #fff;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
}
.k-toaster .k-toast .k-toast-btn-clear[data-v-5e0ed801] {
  order: 1;
  margin-left: auto;
  border: 0;
  color: inherit;
  opacity: 0.45;
  text-decoration: none;
  cursor: pointer;
  background: transparent;
}
.k-toaster .k-toast .k-toast-btn-clear[data-v-5e0ed801]:hover {
  opacity: 0.85;
}
.k-toaster .k-toast .k-toast-btn-clear[data-v-5e0ed801]::before {
  content: "\2715";
}

/* Toaster Variants */
.k-toaster .k-toast.success[data-v-5e0ed801] {
  color: #008038;
  border-color: #8cd9ac;
  background: #ecf9f2;
}
.k-toaster .k-toast.info[data-v-5e0ed801] {
  color: #004a80;
  border-color: #7cc9ff;
  background: #ebf7ff;
}
.k-toaster .k-toast.danger[data-v-5e0ed801] {
  color: #c20d0a;
  border-color: #ff8080;
  background: #fff0f0;
}

/* Toaster Slide Animation */
.slide-enter-active[data-v-5e0ed801],
.slide-leave-active[data-v-5e0ed801] {
  transition: all .4s ease;
}
.slide-enter[data-v-5e0ed801],
.slide-leave-to[data-v-5e0ed801] {
  transform: translate(100%);
}
@media (max-width: 300px) {
.k-toaster[data-v-5e0ed801] {
    width: 100%;
}

<style>
  /* Values */
  :root {
    {% for k, v in each(theme.colors) do %}
      --{{k}}: {{v}};
    {% end %}
  }

  /* Utilities */
  {% for k, v in each(theme.colors) do %}
  .color-{{k}} {
    color: var(--{{k}});
  }

  .bg-{{k}} {
    background-color: var(--{{k}});
  }
  {% end %}

  /* Font Families */
  body {
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol";
    font-family: "{{theme.font('base')}}";
  }
  pre,code,kbd {
    font-family: inherit;
    font-family: "{{theme.font('code')}}"
  }
  h1, h2, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6 {
    font-family: inherit;
    font-family: "{{theme.font('headings')}}"
  }
</style>
